    <title>mysql远程可访问，本地非root无法访问解决方案</title>
    <link href="https://ukhack.github.io/mysql%E7%99%BB%E5%BD%95%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E5%9D%91.html"/>
    <id>https://ukhack.github.io/mysql登录问题的一个坑.html</id>
    <published>2016-12-12T16:00:00.000Z</published>
    <updated>2017-09-07T10:42:09.906Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="mysql远程可访问，本地非root无法访问解决方案"><a href="#mysql远程可访问，本地非root无法访问解决方案" class="headerlink" title="mysql远程可访问，本地非root无法访问解决方案"></a>mysql远程可访问，本地非root无法访问解决方案</h1><h5 id="2016-12-12-星期二"><a href="#2016-12-12-星期二" class="headerlink" title="2016-12-12 星期二"></a>2016-12-12 星期二</h5><p>最近在使用mysql5.5中遇到了一个坑。</p>
<h3 id="发现问题"><a href="#发现问题" class="headerlink" title="发现问题"></a>发现问题</h3><p>通常，在mysql安装完毕后我们并不会使用自带的root用户，以规避爆破的风险。<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">mysql&gt;grant all PRIVILEGES on *.* to zr@&apos;%&apos; identified by &apos;z********6&apos;;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>grant all命令可以为我新建一个用户zr(名字缩写)，并赋予了其root权限。zr用户的主机是%，意味着可以远程登录。<br>关掉puty,我在本地的mysql输入：<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ mysql -h 67.21.*.183 -u zr -p&apos;z********6&apos;;</div><div class="line">mysql&gt;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>可以成功登录。但是打开puty,登录mysql问题来了，给我报了个错<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">Access denied for user &apos;zr&apos;@&apos;localhost&apos; (using password: YES)</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>我试着使用root登录:<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ mysql  -u root -p&apos;**********&apos;;</div><div class="line">mysql&gt;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>这真令人尴尬，root可以本地登录但是我新建的zr不可以登录，但是zr又可以远程登录。</p>
<h3 id="解决问题"><a href="#解决问题" class="headerlink" title="解决问题"></a>解决问题</h3><p>乖乖爬墙，发现一个方案是修改host<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">localhost 127.0.0.1</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>然而无效。基本可以排除并不是解析的问题。<br>登录root查用户：<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ mysql  -u root -p&apos;**********&apos;;</div><div class="line">mysql&gt;select host,user,password from mysql.user where user=&apos;zr&apos;</div><div class="line">+---------+--------+-------------------------------------------+</div><div class="line">| host    | user   | password                                  |</div><div class="line">+---------+--------+-------------------------------------------+</div><div class="line">| %       | zr     | *2CC0511FAC200EDC90EEF9CFC206B07E7BD90F97 |</div><div class="line">+---------+--------+-------------------------------------------+</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>排除用户创建的问题。那么问题到底出在哪？<br>再次查询用户<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ mysql  -u root -p&apos;**********&apos;;</div><div class="line">mysql&gt;select host,user,password from mysql.user where user=&apos;zr&apos;</div><div class="line">+----------+-------+-------------------------------------------+</div><div class="line">| host     | user  | password                                  |</div><div class="line">+----------+-------+-------------------------------------------+</div><div class="line">| localhost| root  | *2CC0511FAC200EDC90EEF9CFC206B07E7BD90F97 |</div><div class="line">| 127.0.0.1| root  | *2CC0511FAC200EDC90EEF9CFC206B07E7BD90F97 |</div><div class="line">| ::1      | root  | *2CC0511FAC200EDC90EEF9CFC206B07E7BD90F97 |</div><div class="line">| localhost|       |                                           |</div><div class="line">| %        | zr    | *2CC0511FAC200EDC90EEF9CFC206B07E7BD90F97 |</div><div class="line">+----------+-------+-------------------------------------------+</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>看到这里我想你们应该知道问题在哪了，没错。<br>问题出在第三行，原理后面说。<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ mysql  -u root -p&apos;**********&apos;;</div><div class="line">mysql&gt;select host,user,password from mysql.user where user=&apos;zr&apos;</div><div class="line">+----------+-------+-------------------------------------------+</div><div class="line">| host     | user  | password                                  |</div><div class="line">+----------+-------+-------------------------------------------+</div><div class="line">| localhost| root  | *2CC0511FAC200EDC90EEF9CFC206B07E7BD90F97 |</div><div class="line">| 127.0.0.1| root  | *2CC0511FAC200EDC90EEF9CFC206B07E7BD90F97 |</div><div class="line">| ::1      | root  | *2CC0511FAC200EDC90EEF9CFC206B07E7BD90F97 |</div><div class="line">| localhost|       |                                           |</div><div class="line">| %        | zr    | *2CC0511FAC200EDC90EEF9CFC206B07E7BD90F97 |</div><div class="line">+----------+-------+-------------------------------------------+</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>进行修复：<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">mysql&gt;delete from user where user=&apos;&apos;</div><div class="line">Query OK, 2 rows affected (0.00 sec)</div><div class="line">mysql&gt;flush privileges;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>重新登录成功</p>
<h3 id="原理"><a href="#原理" class="headerlink" title="原理"></a>原理</h3><p>其实mysql权限认证的修改就是对mysql.user这张表的增删改查。当我们登录时，mysql会去user表遍历一遍，以找到的第一个匹配项匹配，不再向下匹配。找不到匹配的就会阻断用户的请求。而我们看到所有用户中的是有匿名用户存在的。<br>之所以root可以登录成功是因为localhost+root排在第一个匹配位，理所当然的可以登录成功。而在zr前面是有一个user=’’的匿名用户，它的匹配优先级高于zr，这导致我无法用zr登录，哪怕登录了也是匿名用户。最终方法就是删掉匿名用户，原理是不是很简单。</p>
